snippet.title: Launch Trailer | Fae Farm
snippet.description:
Your magical journey begins here. 🌱 

Step into a world of enchantment of Azoria, where every corner holds whispers of magic. Immerse yourself in a realm of enchanted homesteads, mystical creatures, whimsical quests, and experience the magic in #FaeFarm.✨

Fae Farm is available September 8, 2023, on Nintendo Switch and PC. Learn more about Fae Farm: https://fae.farm/45LLke9

Join our Discord here: https://discord.gg/Qsz9vsS6uw
Join us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/FaeFarm/
Join us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/faefarm/
Join us on TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@faefarm
